parameters:
I must have fallen into a trap. I let my guard
down.

I was just sent back to the entrance. But did
Hoffman find out?

I wonder... It seems like the defensive magic just
activated automatically.
I hope she's okay... Wait, where is Amelia?
She's not here. Was she sent to a different place?

There's no time to re-enter the workshop. Besides,
I don't know where she is.
All we can do is pray for her safety.

Even if we get caught by Professor Hoffman,
there's no choice but to abandon her.

Don't joke around, there's no way we can abandon
Amelia!
Then all we can do is pray.

(If it's Amelia's ability, there's no way she'll
lose to Hoffman.)

(It's okay... Besides, it's not like we've been
caught by Hoffman yet.)
(If worst comes to worst, we can start over...)
I'm going back to my room.

Well, I don't think they'll expel us just for
entering the workshop without permission.
If anything happens, please report it tomorrow.
